## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the inherent biases present in philosophical and ethical discussions. The complexity of the topic means that not all perspectives can be fully explored in a single report. Additionally, the ethical considerations surrounding meat consumption are deeply personal and culturally specific, which may not be fully captured in the available literature.

